<item>
            <title>[HIVE-1046] Pass build.dir.hive and other properties to subant</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-1046</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently we are not passing properties like &quot;build.dir.hive&quot; etc to subant.&lt;br/&gt;
We should do that, otherwise setting &quot;build.dir.hive&quot; is not useful.&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
